verses.verse: A <S%H7892>Song<s%> of <S%H4609>degrees<s%> of <S%H1732>David<s%>. Behold, how <S%H2896>good<s%> and how <S%H5273>pleasant<s%> it is for <S%H251>brethren<s%> to <S%H3427>dwell<s%> <S%H3162>together<s%> in <S%H3162>unity<s%>! together: Heb. even together
